TITLE: Advanced Request Routing in C#
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to implement advanced request routing with header modification and resource type filtering.
SOURCE: https://github.com/microsoft/playwright/blob/main/docs/src/release-notes-csharp.md#2025-04-22_snippet_21

LANGUAGE: csharp
CODE:
```
// Remove a header from all requests.
await page.RouteAsync("**/*", async route =>
{
    var headers = route.Request.Headers;
    headers.Remove("X-Secret");
    await route.ContinueAsync(new() { Headers = headers });
});

// Abort all images.
await page.RouteAsync("**/*", async route =>
{
    if (route.Request.ResourceType == "image")
    {
        await route.AbortAsync();
    }
    else
    {
        await route.FallbackAsync();
    }
});
```

